<outro>
[Am]当天|dang tian [G]边那颗|bian na ke [C]星出|xing chu [C]现|xian
[]你可|ni ke [F]知我|zhi wo [G]又开始想|you kai shi xiang [C]念|nian
[]有多|you duo [F]少爱|shao ai [G]恋|lian
[]今生|jin sheng [Em]无处安|wu chu an [Am]放|fang
[]冥冥|ming ming [F]中什|zhong shen [G]么已改|me yi gai [Am]变|bian
[]月光|yue guang [F]如春|ru chun [G]风拂|feng fu [Am]面|mian